\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khu v\u1ef1c Signature Lounge, v\u1edbi c&aacute;c \u0111\u1eb7c quy\u1ec1n g\u1ed3m: b\u1eefa s&aacute;ng t\u1ef1 ch\u1ecdn, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng kh&ocirc;ng c\u1ed3n v&agrave; r\u01b0\u1ee3u vang s\u1ee7i trong ng&agrave;y, v&agrave; s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng c&oacute; c\u1ed3n k&egrave;m \u0103n nh\u1eb9 t\u1ef1 ch\u1ecdn v&agrave;o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48t2cn57 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-48t2cn5r fg-row row     fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-48t2cn65 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><h2 class=\"ffb-id-48t2cn67 fg-heading text-left    fg-text-dark\">QUY\u1ec0N L\u1ee2I &amp; TI\u1ec6N NGHI<\/h2><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48t2cn68 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-48t2cn6a fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p>- Ph&ograve;ng kh&ocirc;ng kh&oacute;i thu\u1ed1c<\/p>\n<p>- C&oacute; quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Signature Lounge<\/p>\n<p>- C&oacute; \u0111i\u1ec1u h&ograve;a kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute;<\/p>\n<p>- Trang b\u1ecb m&aacute;y pha c&agrave; ph&ecirc; Nespresso<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48t2cn6b fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-48t2cn6d fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p>- Trang b\u1ecb m&aacute;y s\u1ea5y t&oacute;c<\/p>\n<p>- Trang b\u1ecb k&eacute;t s\u1eaft an to&agrave;n<\/p>\n<p>- D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 spa (c&oacute; t&iacute;nh ph&iacute;)<\/p>\n<p>- Mini Bar (c&oacute; t&iacute;nh ph&iacute;)<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-4ov6lm6f buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/be.synxis.com\/?Hotel=3592&#038;room=E1K\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-xs    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">\u0110\u1eb6T PH\u00d2NG<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/